11 An Act relating to public finance; enacting the State
Department of Education Spending Transparency Act;
12 defining terms; requiring Internet-based portal;
prescribing required content related to expenditures
13 by state government; imposing duties on governmental
entities; authorizing the Office of Management and
14 Enterprise Services to include certain information;
providing for annual agreements; prohibiting release
15 of confidential information; requiring standards for
reporting; providing for administrative rules;
16 prescribing requirements for website displays;
providing for codification; and providing an
17 effective date.
